Title: DOUBLE PRECISION
Feature:
DOUBLE PRECISION[(M,D)] [SIGNED | UNSIGNED | ZEROFILL]
REAL[(M,D)] [SIGNED | UNSIGNED | ZEROFILL]
Description: REAL and DOUBLE PRECISION are synonyms for DOUBLE.

Exception: If the REAL_AS_FLOAT SQL mode is enabled, 
REAL is a synonym for FLOAT rather than 
DOUBLE.
